					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Natalie Zutter</h4>
												<p><strong>Natalie Zutter</strong> is a Brooklyn-based playwright and pop culture critic whose work has appeared on Tor.com, NPR Books, <em>Den of Geek</em>, and elsewhere. Find her on Twitter <a class="external" href="https://twitter.com/nataliezutter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@nataliezutter</a>.</p>
